<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Fur_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Phonology">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Phonology">Phonology</span></h2>
<p>The consonantal phonemes are:</p>
<table class="IPA wikitable" style="text-align: center;">
